txt.en: Orc Captains can be found within the port of Harlond.\n\nYou should defeat Orc Captains within the port of Harlond.

'There are two captains of the enemy in the Harlond. Their defeat will most certainly cause disorder within the ranks. It is important that these Orc captains are defeated before Aragorn and his men make landfall.'
Orc Captains can be found within the port of the Harlond.\n\nYou should defeat Orc Captains within the port of the Harlond.
Aragorn will need the port of the Harlond cleared if he and his men are to make landfall with haste.
